OL,3,CTributes paid to teenager who died
OL,4,Cfollowing fatal bike crash
OL,6,FThe family of a 16-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied when his bike collided with a car
OL,8,Fin Cardiff have paid tribute to him.
OL,10,FSouth Wales Police are continuing to
OL,11,Finvestigate the death of Miracle
OL,12,FOladoyinbo after he died following the
OL,13,Fincident on Penarth Road at its
OL,14,Fjunction with Clare Road in
OL,15,FGrangetown, on Wednesday 25 March.
OL,17,FHis family have said that Miracle "was
OL,18,Fa beacon of joy and compassion, a 16-
OL,19,Fyear-old whose life was defined by a
OL,20,Fprofound love for God and an
OL,21,Funwavering commitment to his faith.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
