OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F466A1774976748
OL,3,CTributes paid to teenager who died
OL,4,Cfollowing fatal bike crash
OL,6,F"A gifted musician, he didn't just
OL,7,Fplay music; he used his talents as a
OL,8,Fministry to uplift spirits and bring
OL,9,Fcomfort to everyone around him.
OL,11,F"To know Miracle was to be touched by
OL,12,Fhis warmth and inspired by his grace.
OL,13,FWhile his life was tragically cut
OL,14,Fshort, the melody of his kind heart
OL,15,Fand the strength of his testimony will
OL,16,Fresonate forever in the hearts of the
OL,17,Ffamily and community who loved him so
OL,18,Fdearly."
